ZH: 我家的窗户很大。
EN: The window in my house is very big.

ZH: 窗户外面看起来很美。
EN: The view outside the window looks very beautiful.

ZH: 这个窗户需要清洁一下。
EN: This window needs to be cleaned.

ZH: 窗户上挂着一幅风景画。
EN: There is a landscape painting hanging on the window.

ZH: 窗户被遮住了，所以屋内很暗。
EN: The window is covered, so the room is dark.

ZH: 我在窗户外面看到了一只小鸟。
EN: I saw a little bird outside the window.

ZH: 窗户上有一层薄膜。
EN: There is a thin film on the window.

ZH: 窗户玻璃上有很多水珠。
EN: There are many water droplets on the window glass.

ZH: 我总是喜欢坐在窗户旁边看书。
EN: I always like to sit by the window and read.

ZH: 窗户外面飘来一阵清新的风。
EN: A fresh breeze is blowing in from outside the window.

ZH: 这扇窗户很难打开。
EN: This window is difficult to open.

ZH: 他坐在窗户边上思考人生。
EN: He sits by the window contemplating life.

ZH: 窗户外面传来孩子们的欢声笑语。
EN: Children's laughter can be heard coming from outside the window.

ZH: 窗户上有一只小猫躺在晒太阳。
EN: There is a little cat lying in the sun on the window.

ZH: 我们家的窗户是双层隔音的。
EN: The windows in our house are double glazed for soundproofing.

ZH: 窗户已经关上了，请不要打扰。
EN: The window is already closed, please do not disturb.

ZH: 每当下雨，窗户就会漏水。
EN: Whenever it rains, the window leaks water.

ZH: 窗户上贴着一张纸条，上面写着“请勿打扰”。
EN: There is a note pasted on the window that says "Do not disturb".

ZH: 夜晚的窗户是一道风景线。
EN: The window at night is a beautiful sight.

ZH: 现代设计的窗户非常简洁而美观。
EN: Modern designed windows are very simple and beautiful.
